{"tid":1628800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想像下日日要提早落車行返屋企，市民感覺會點？","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T05:45:22.000Z","uid":78184,"like":26,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a037eedd55344245fd0521ff2c6ac0e7152260f4","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"各位手足，我地每一個人都想運動成功、想爭取民主、自由。由六月行到而家，我地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理、勇武合流，不篤不割，互相配合合作，加上政府、警察犯錯，呢場運動先可以浩浩蕩蕩行到今天。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下我講既野，未必個個岩聽，但如果覺得我係五毛搞分化，可以起底睇我以往的Post。我見解唔一定岩，但希望引發大家一齊思考點樣做得更好。<br />\n<br />\n我們的勇武抗爭行動，短短四個月，由被動式抗狗升級到主動為救手足而打狗，呢一點市民相對接受，只要唔好主動「殺狗」就得，因為廣大市民都認同警暴濫權的問題。<br />\n<br />\n至於對付中資、賣港商店，由最初噴漆、拎飛霸位，變成打爛玻璃設施甚至火魔法，大家就要小心唔好傷及無辜同埋附近有民居就要留手。<br />\n<br />\n最重要一點，設路障和交通問題。發覺呢幾日大家好踴躍設路障令交通癱瘓。其實RB的初心係防狗，但近日的RB變左非常擾民。4/10星期五晚上八點幾開始，親眼目睹東九龍區大量市民要提早落車步行回家。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有d市民係老年人，有d係下班族塞車都塞左三個鐘，你要佢再行15-30分鐘返屋企，你估佢地辛唔辛苦、燥唔燥、火唔火？</span></span>可能入面甚至有自己手足係想先返屋企再出黎幫拖。<br />\n<br />\n我本人當然好明白，呢場抗爭，無一個人可以置身事外。但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">設身處地，有些中間、淺黃，可能理解以前大家的憤怒而包容針對政府、警隊甚至藍絲的行為。但並非代表佢地會(已經無可能認同)包容一些影響到佢「返屋企」的破壞性的行動。坦白講，如果而家經常性示威都搞到商店縱火、堵路擠塞，令到日常民生有重大影響，連屋企都返唔到，大家諗諗，試問邊個市民會接受？</span></span>當呢種極影響民生的行動過多的時候，班中間派會唔會反感？仲會唔會支持我地？<br />\n<br />\n當班中間派都轉色、支持警隊執法平息亂局時，我地無咁大量的民氣、民意作後援，對場運動係好定壞？希望大家三思！<br />\n<br />\n當然，政府透過緊急法訂立禁蒙面法，都講到明希望做到和理非「堅決」同勇武割蓆，甚至社區對話的目的都係想和理非割。所以我希望無論如何，大家都要核彈都唔割。但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懇請每位手足都要思考我地有無進步、改善的空間，要智勇相全、和勇輪流上場</span></span>，先可以長玩長有！打仗，總不能一味靠衝。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後，今天全民口罩大遊行，街頭相見。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7c8a5e38f5dca2389e6299415bca9b5b7187b8ad","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"fc2f38a946d8b182d581c84b4244a96567bd7507","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"bf8cbfaa21986da61c55dc3c51aa5952fd441074","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a71536ca4f6e479b50e4b9b6c2c26a6105b20f6b","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:45:46.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"323c39f98a52471393af38ec38148bf187d563ff","tid":1628800,"uid":6310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"黨鐵必須屎"},{"pid":"2f3fb77bf60a2dc77615f25d2b42ad85a4f997b7","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"dca3f97810af706bb9dc3dd2359561e9d7628e52","tid":1628800,"uid":273318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"出緊去喇陣間見"},{"pid":"7bc121f106650c8043fdc4a6cc001e956fb138b3","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"babb11613843dc210543aeff56eb2c7b40f96100","tid":1628800,"uid":257539,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"市民咪會覺得政府仆街囉"},{"pid":"abd809fdc0c5d77a323e0c77222073d3bd0ccb44","tid":1628800,"uid":68868,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"準備緊去火星抗爭"},{"pid":"40a1f54ef60f2e7c1bc4596b2493e189f0195a30","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"323c39f98a52471393af38ec38148bf187d563ff","tid":1628800,"uid":6310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"黨鐵必須屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"認同，但唔好令到黨鐘又死，路面又死<br />\n經常要市民落車行一大段路返屋企，結果對我地觀感一定差，有害無利"},{"pid":"ecaf6910e228df10952a04e7322bd90ff06283cf","tid":1628800,"uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:47:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9418f824030a0fc5363b927c9153f761bd755e64","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"babb11613843dc210543aeff56eb2c7b40f96100","tid":1628800,"uid":257539,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"市民咪會覺得政府仆街囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:48:44.000Z","msg":"你可以試下出去問下非同溫層的中間派，甚至淺黃父母長輩睇睇。<br />\n雖然大家知道政府仆街，但不代表支持呢種破壞性的行動，因為太影響無辜的市民日常生活。只會慢慢俾政府反cup"},{"pid":"8c9b16c9fcbb0bdbff81448d6a75c17d96ff2ed0","tid":1628800,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"如果個政府已經到開實彈射細路民個程度，我重介意我返工麻煩左，我會覺得我好無人性"},{"pid":"c203fe0eac17ccdd4e249f97766634fc84bf6ab7","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"408f2388ffdf50b4d31ecf384280fb71713acbd0","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abd809fdc0c5d77a323e0c77222073d3bd0ccb44","tid":1628800,"uid":68868,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"準備緊去火星抗爭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:49:12.000Z","msg":"希望三思<br />\nPlay smart"},{"pid":"e3c126ac6b978d9e9c0792f5709751048b88d3bd","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:49:22.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"f56699536ed181b1a94f7d8135db63e1f99be618","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dca3f97810af706bb9dc3dd2359561e9d7628e52","tid":1628800,"uid":273318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"出緊去喇陣間見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:49:39.000Z","msg":"好，一陣街頭相見"},{"pid":"f5b188ac2b4b5630a1aaff46eb82b0ab048c7c4f","tid":1628800,"uid":38768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:50:36.000Z","msg":"如果為左你口中既辛苦, 要為手足增加風險<br />\n咁你不如去解釋點解要咁做"},{"pid":"c9583f3f62ce6a2757615d33397b7dcf853cd691","tid":1628800,"uid":201427,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"如果有朋友咁諗<br />\n我會解釋俾佢聽個問題係政府同黨鐵到<br />\n如果佢地唔理解同咁都要埋怨既<br />\n佢地只係一班坐係到咩都唔想付出就想得到公義同自由既人"},{"pid":"41ef97804438c9c2a8f4652eb92eb1738601bdc2","tid":1628800,"uid":13187,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:50:53.000Z","msg":"琴日天水圍有手足打爛馬路指揮燈<br />\n其實我唔太欣賞，我睇唔透目的係乜？<br />\n但基於尊重前線<br />\n唔想當面質問自己人<br />\n只想賽後檢討"},{"pid":"88400fa3e37846308586f50d4f20cd83d846d23b","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8c9b16c9fcbb0bdbff81448d6a75c17d96ff2ed0","tid":1628800,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"如果個政府已經到開實彈射細路民個程度，我重介意我返工麻煩左，我會覺得我好無人性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:50:53.000Z","msg":"要考慮一下，唔係每個人都會將兩件事連結埋一齊。<br />\n中間派可能認同開實彈好仆街，但一樣唔想連屋企都返唔到。"},{"pid":"33b52aa60245b1fb4fa47fcfa526778dcd65bb32","tid":1628800,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"bace759563a05c35b91d50a9e3448419dd57545d","tid":1628800,"uid":322637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:51:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}